  "description": "Deep antagonistic quality review of `hx-button` (T1-01). 6/6 libraries ship this — it must be flawless.\n\nReview every file in `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-button/` with a critical eye.\n\n**Audit areas:**\n1. TypeScript — strict compliance, no `any`, all variants/sizes typed, exported types match CEM\n2. Accessibility — WCAG 2.1 AA, `role=\"button\"` correct, keyboard (Enter/Space activate, Tab focus), disabled state, loading state aria, axe-core pass\n3. Tests — all variants (primary/secondary/ghost/danger/outline), all sizes (sm/md/lg), loading state, disabled, icon slots, form submission, 80%+ coverage\n4. Storybook — all variants with controls, interactive demos working\n5. CSS — only `--hx-*` tokens, CSS parts (button, label, icon) exposed, no hardcoded values, focus ring visible\n6. Performance — bundle size < 5KB min+gz\n7. Drupal — renders from Twig, CDN-importable, no JS framework dependency\n\n**Output:** Write findings to `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-button/AUDIT.md` with severity (P0/P1/P2) and file:line references. DO NOT fix — document only. Commit AUDIT.md as your PR.",
